{"tid":700264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"驗屍報告指艾斯托利本有機獲救","createTime":"2018-06-13T08:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T09:49:20.000Z","uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24bcf94e6ffc58d344523e8d2382a8c18c90df25","tid":700264,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:13:46.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=HAZdIaBCQoHtnCf8pRKwwDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9894684f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】已故費倫天拿隊長艾斯托利的最新驗屍報告指，艾斯托利在心臟停頓前曾心跳加速，最終死亡。<br />\n<br />\n根據意大利各大傳媒報道，前費倫天拿隊長艾斯托利（Davide Astori）可能患有心臟病，但一直未被發現。最初在艾斯托利逝世的時候，有報告指他是因心律過慢，最終心跳停頓而死亡，在睡夢中暴斃。<br />\n<br />\n不過，最新的驗屍報告指出，艾斯托利的死因是心跳過快，這意味著他死前可能已經醒過來，如果有人在他身邊，有機會獲救。現在有關當局正在調查這個問題是否可以及早診斷，避免悲劇發生。<br />\n<br />\n31歲的艾斯托利於今年3月4日上午，被發現倒斃在酒店房間裡，估計前一晚已不幸身亡。費倫天拿其後宣佈成立基金，旨在協助艾斯托利的女兒Vittoria成長。"},{"pid":"3ded0821c7536c427f027f6c976c5c37f4a0e091","tid":700264,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d3dc97f8fedb049928242de5b01f5e1be260ac","tid":700264,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"bc4874f92447fa0464a916eda48428a10362715f","tid":700264,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"點解運動員都可以check唔到心有事？"},{"pid":"cfab37cee8fece02bbaab0048b744c1b1df786db","tid":700264,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc4874f92447fa0464a916eda48428a10362715f","tid":700264,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"點解運動員都可以check唔到心有事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"隱性就好難"},{"pid":"80077ff7850449dd4ef5a397c7983a43d7461f1e","tid":700264,"uid":114014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}